title: Tramp Twitt: No big win in Georgia for #Team Kraken
subtitle: It has been established that the claim that Tramp's legal supporters won a "large judicial order" in an attempt to reverse the results of the elections in Georgia was short-lived.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The legal supporters of Tramp won a "big judicial order" in their quest to reverse the results of the elections in Georgia.
